@startuml
title Widget Tree - Level 1

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class "Root widget" as Root
class "Panel widget" as Panel
class "Button widget" as Button
class "Text widget" as Text

Root o-- Panel
Panel o-- Button
Panel o-- Text

note right of Root
A window starts with a root widget.
You can add child widgets to build
an interface as a tree.
end note

note bottom of Panel
Moving, hiding, or disabling a parent
can affect the widgets inside it.
end note

@enduml
